parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning backup camera can cause a safety hazard by distracting the driver with a live video feed on the screen while driving forward, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The backup camera remains on in neutral and drive modes
displaying live video on the screen
even when not in reverse gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can pose a safety risk by preventing the driver from alerting other drivers or pedestrians in emergency situations.
symptoms: The horn periodically quits working
sometimes for days at a time
and may randomly start working again; the horn may also lose volume or stop working altogether
especially in cold temperatures.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system issues can pose a safety risk by causing malfunctions in various systems, including the backup camera, horn, and steering, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The backup camera remains on in neutral and drive modes
the horn periodically quits working
and the steering makes a noise on occasion when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning infotainment system can cause a safety risk by distracting the driver and losing access to important features like navigation and visual maps.
symptoms: The Apple CarPlay or display loses connection
causing the driver to lose attention from the road and access to visual maps
especially in nighttime and snowy conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning seat belt system can lead to inadequate restraint, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt light remains illuminated even when the seat is empty
the seat belt is too tight and constricting
the seat belt inadvertently disconnects while driving
the rear passenger seatbelt is constantly locked and does not expand to provide adequate space.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty lane assist system can cause the vehicle to drift or steer unexpectedly, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The lane assist system causes the wheel to shift while driving
the vehicle wants to crash into a wall or drift out of its lane.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A reduced fuel tank capacity can lead to increased fuel stops, inconvenience, and potential safety risks if the vehicle runs out of fuel in hazardous conditions.
symptoms: The fuel tank capacity has decreased
resulting in fewer miles per fill-up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A constantly honking horn can be a distraction and a nuisance, potentially leading to accidents or other safety issues.
symptoms: The horn is constantly honking and not working properly.
